#

Savory Pork Meat Gravy with Creamy Mashed Potatoes

$12.99
650 kcal

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-Optional

Tags:

Comfort FoodHeartySavory

Description

A rich and hearty pork meat gravy served over velvety mashed potatoes, perfect for a comforting dinner.

Ingredients

  • Pork shoulder: 2 lbs
  • Onion: 1 large, diced
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Chicken broth: 2 cups
  • Flour: 1/4 cup
  • Butter: 4 tablespoons (or olive oil for dairy-free)
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
  • Mashed potatoes (prepared): 4 cups
  • Thyme: 1 teaspoon (optional)
